doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Portfolio of Janvi Ahuja')
        meta(name='author', content='Janvi Ahuja')

        title Janvi Ahuja - Data Science & Mathematics Portfolio

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/img/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Saira+Extra+Condensed:500,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Muli:400,400i,800,800i', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#sideNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-primary.fixed-top
            a.navbar-brand.js-scroll-trigger(href='#page-top')
                span.d-block.d-lg-none Janvi Ahuja
                span.d-none.d-lg-block
                    img.img-fluid.img-profile.rounded-circle.mx-auto.mb-2(src='assets/img/profile.jpg', alt='Janvi Ahuja')
            button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                span.navbar-toggler-icon
            #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                ul.navbar-nav
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#experience') Experience
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#education') Education
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#skills') Skills
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#interests') Interests

        // Page Content
        .container-fluid.p-0

            // About
            section#about.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h1.mb-0
                        | Janvi
                        span.text-primary Ahuja
                    .subheading.mb-5
                        | Data Science & Mathematics | Penn State University
                        br
                        | (814) 826-8392 · 
                        a(href='mailto:ahujajanvi08@gmail.com') ahujajanvi08@gmail.com
                        br
                        a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/janviahuja', target='_blank') LinkedIn Profile
                    p.lead.mb-5
                        | Growing up, I was always fascinated by how people make predictions—whether in sports, markets, or daily life. When I first encountered coding, I was captivated by how data science allows us to uncover patterns hidden within the data we already have.
                        br
                        | At Penn State, I’m pursuing a dual major in Data Science and Mathematics, blending my analytical mindset with my passion for understanding human behavior through data. My experience spans roles in marketing analytics and education, where I translate complex data into actionable insights.

            hr.m-0

            // Experience
            section#experience.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Experience

                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between.mb-5
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 Marketing Data Analyst Intern
                            .subheading.mb-3 Birla Limited
                            p
                                | Conducted marketing data analysis to optimize outreach and customer segmentation strategies, leading to a 15% increase in campaign effectiveness.
                                br
                                | Delivered data-driven recommendations to guide strategic decision-making.
                        .flex-shrink-0
                            span.text-primary June 2024 - August 2024

                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between.mb-5
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 Learning Assistant
                            .subheading.mb-3 Department of Mathematics, Penn State University
                            p
                                | Led student discussions and tutoring sessions to simplify complex calculus concepts.
                                br
                                | Conducted presentations and office hours, bridging gaps in student understanding.
                        .flex-shrink-0
                            span.text-primary Jan 2023 - May 2023

            hr.m-0

            // Education
            section#education.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Education
                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between.mb-5
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 The Pennsylvania State University
                            .subheading.mb-3 Dual Major: Data Science & Mathematics
                            div Applied Data Sciences & System Analysis
                            p GPA: 3.41, Dean’s List (5/7 semesters)
                        .flex-shrink-0
                            span.text-primary August 2021 - May 2025

            hr.m-0

            // Skills
            section#skills.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Skills
                    ul.list-inline.dev-icons
                        li.list-inline-item Python, SQL, R, Java, C++, JavaScript
                        li.list-inline-item NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib, Excel, PySpark
                        li.list-inline-item Data Analytics, Statistical Modeling, Machine Learning

            hr.m-0

            // Interests
            section#interests.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Interests
                    p
                        | Huge sports fan, especially cricket, and love staying updated with global events.
                        br
                        | Passionate about fashion and data trends, always exploring the intersection between human behavior and analytics.

